{"tid":2264237,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"8.31事件7個月遞竹枝協助堵路 跟車工認罪 保釋候判","createTime":"2020-10-30T13:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T15:23:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0e25ace2ab43bc60469436b0fba12b47082fe10a","tid":2264237,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:10:39.000Z","msg":"8.31太子站事件7個月當晚，有市民響應網上號召到屯門堵路，警方到場驅散，在附近拘捕一名跟車工人，工人承認幫手傳送竹枝協助堵路。他今在屯門裁判法院承認在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，案件押後判刑，被告獲准保釋候判。<br />\n<br />\n辯方今求情稱，被告是家庭經濟支柱，當時響應網上號召，有份運送竹枝，但沒有親手將竹放至路面。<br />\n<br />\n辯方指本案案情較同類案件輕微，涉案時間不長，範圍不大，僅四輛車被阻，報警投訴堵路的司機花了一分鐘便繞過路障，被告願向受影響人士致歉。署理主任裁判官張潔宜將案件押後至11月13日，索取社會服務令報告才判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/U56I2E5IAJEMBN7LELEUYM42LM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FU56I2E5IAJEMBN7LELEUYM42LM%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdl6E%2F45TZQXVIGc6puLiPLc%3D&h=1191f1b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201030%2FU56I2E5IAJEMBN7LELEUYM42LM%2F&h=c9e75db2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201030/U56I2E5IAJEMBN7LELEUYM42LM/</a>"},{"pid":"181624ecc6fa6026ae485ab0056ace746b61833b","tid":2264237,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3c515063953c21e1a015c37136dfd7d58d9dc4","tid":2264237,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T13:13:20.000Z","msg":"署理主任裁判官張潔宜將案件押後至11月13日，索取社會服務令報告才判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n竟然唔洗還押？"},{"pid":"1e4b1f9cfb27bd09f35ac9ef2a50567969c96421","tid":2264237,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0b3c515063953c21e1a015c37136dfd7d58d9dc4","tid":2264237,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":